      "span_text": "Thus, DOV 21,947 produces antidepressant-like activity in the rodent forced swim and tail suspension tests.  The success, however, of this compound-as well as the strategy and benefit of combing inhibition of all three monoamines into a single molecule-is still awaiting evaluation in human patients."
